{"id":"paltite","term":"Paltite","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>The designation of one of David’s heroes (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 23:26\">2 Sam. 23:26</a>); called also the Pelonite (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 11:27\">1 Chr. 11:27</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Samuel 23:26","1 Chronicles 11:27"]}